    <h1 id="what" class="bold offset">What Is HackMizzou? <a class="pull-right" href="http://2014.hackmizzou.com"><button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">HackMizzou Site</button></a></h1>

    <p class="friendly">

      HackMizzou is a weekend long tech conference where participants start with an idea and leave with a product. HackMizzou encourages students to learn new technologies, experiment, and innovate in a risk free environment. Students also have the ability to apply to internships/full-time jobs, enjoy conference-like tech talks, and a weekend of free food and transportation.
    </p>

